document.discussion_title: Kumba Health Launches Consumer Subscription Model for Healthcare Portal
document.topic_text: Kumba Health Launches Consumer Subscription Model for Healthcare Portal Monday, 25 April 2016 ( 25 minutes ago ) LOS ANGELES--(BUSINESS WIRE)--#concierge--Direct-pay healthcare startup Kumba Health launches subscription service for the 99% to have access to top doctors. New healthcare model being called "concierge light."
